<l>paṇivuṭaiya ṉiṉcola ṉātal oruvaṟk</l>
<l>aṇiyalla maṟṟup piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To be humble and possessed of sweet speech is one's</l>
